;Time: 19:30 UTC, Mondays (current)
;Length: Approx. 1 hour (estimated)
;Schedule: [http://www.google.com/calendar/embed?src=9lnuvubqkdssdmqtvvk60bl0nk%40group.calendar.google.com Google Calendar]
